description:
The Python IDE for Professional Developers

Intelligent Python IDE with refactorings, debugger, code completion, on-the-fly code analysis and coding productivity orientation
- PyCharm can now install Poetry for you: PY-65295
- Debugger compatibility with matplotlib==3.9.1.post1 is fixed: PY-75115
- Databricks plugin uses IDE proxy settings from now on: PY-75405
- We bundled django-stubs in PyCharm for better Django code insight: PY-76629
And more! Check all new changes in the release notes.
